.header
    .header__top
        %h1.header__top--name
            = link_to "タイケツ", root_path, class: "toppage"
    .header__middle
        %p.header__middle--sentence
            いつも宿敵、ライバルとして憎み合い、争う合う二人。
            %br/
            たまには言いたいことを遠慮なく吐き出してみませんか？
        %p.header__middle--button
            = link_to "もっと詳しく", root_path, class: "btn"
    .header__bottom
        %ul.header__bottom--links
            %li.list
                = link_to "https://www.facebook.com/" do
                    = fa_icon "facebook", class: "icon"
            %li.list
                = link_to "https://twitter.com/" do
                    = fa_icon "twitter", class: "icon"
            %li.list
                = link_to "http://b.hatena.ne.jp/" do
                    = fa_icon "bold", class: "icon"